g.text: : The Other Side of the City
: The Room is Dark and Gloomy
: A Peaceful Day in Santa Fe
: A Crocodile's Tear In The Rain
: Texture Poem for the Moons of Stars
Following the release of his Music For Clouds LP, Voiski presents Sick Parrots, a compilation of 13 forgotten items, aborted projects, alternative
versions and exclusive tracks. Thirteen Impossible pieces to question the notion of releasability of a track, thus attempting to enlighten about the
making of a record. A bundle of artist indecisions genuinely gathered on a CD coming out in June on Voiski's SUPER 95.
